      State Water Resources Control Board and Regional Water Quality Control
      Boards (SWRCB/RWQCBs) provides equal employment opportunity for all
      persons without regard to age, gender, race, color, religion, national
      origin, political affiliation, ancestry, marital status, gender
      orientation, or disability.



